Package: mobileRNA
Type: Package
Title: Explore RNA mobilome & population-scale changes
Version: 0.99.14
Authors@R: c(person("Katie", "Jeynes-Cupper", 
    email = "kej031@student.bham.ac.uk", role = c("aut", "cre"), 
    comment= "https://orcid.org/0009-0000-1350-1371"),
    person("Marco", "Catoni", email = "m.catoni@bham.ac.uk", role = "aut", 
    comment= "https://orcid.org/0000-0002-3258-2522"))
Description: The mobileRNA package allows for the identifcation of mobile  
  RNA molecules in plant graft systems or other chimeric systems, and supports
  typical sRNAseq analysis between treatment and control conditions. As input, 
  mobileRNA can utilise sRNAseq or mRNAseq data types.
